19:25.122 --> 19:28.410
Ah, lion, elephant, buffalo, leopard and...

19:28.501 --> 19:29.866
Shit.

19:29.960 --> 19:31.996
- Rhino.
- Rhino.

19:32.088 --> 19:34.750
Oh, I hope we see a rhino.
Jack, do you think we'll see a rhino?

19:34.840 --> 19:36.000
- Thank you.
- We will.

19:36.092 --> 19:38.504
We will see a rhino. I promise.

19:38.594 --> 19:41.461
Whoo. Big promise.

19:41.555 --> 19:43.784
- We just have to find them.
- What the brochure said to us.

19:43.808 --> 19:46.720
- Obviously, that wouldn't lie.
- Never.

19:47.895 --> 19:50.637
Oh. Oh, my goodness. Okay.

19:50.731 --> 19:52.392
- What do you feel, Jack?
- I feel like...

19:52.483 --> 19:55.145
- I feel like we're in Africa.
- Yeah, well.

19:55.236 --> 19:56.976
Get ready for our day.

19:57.071 --> 19:59.424
