a word with you?

20:08.958 --> 20:10.289
Yeah, of course, of course.

20:13.212 --> 20:14.748
See, Mr. Halsey,

20:14.839 --> 20:17.706
the safari is not part
of your particular package.

20:17.800 --> 20:20.963
