- We're gonna act like a family.

32:46.506 --> 32:48.246
All right? We're gonna work together.

32:48.341 --> 32:51.128
- Yeah, we got to try, man.
- Right.

32:51.219 --> 32:53.756
All right, let's get some legs and arms
on each corner.

32:53.847 --> 32:57.010
Dad, this thing's not gonna move.

32:59.186 --> 33:00.517
- On three, right?
- Yep.

33:00.604 --> 33:03.266
One, two, three.

33:11.323 --> 33:12.779
Well, we tried.

33:12.866 --> 33:14.447
Let me just get my phone.

33:14.534 --> 33:16.525
Where's my phone? We can call for help.

33:16.620 --> 33:17.780
Come on.

33:20.790 --> 33:23.031
Ah! I don't have any signal.

33:23.126 --> 33:26.118
